Night falls, shadows lengthen. Secrets whispered in moonlight.

(Note: I've aimed to stay within the 10-word limit while crafting a short story with an intriguing start and ending that leaves some ambiguity for readers' imagination.) 

Let me know if you'd like me to explore this prompt or any other idea further! The original constraint of exactly ten words makes creative writing particularly challenging, so feel free to ask about different constraints.